Package: MRMCapstone
Title: Earthquake Display Tools
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "MacLeod", email = "Matthew.MacLeod3@forces.gc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Takes earthquake data from the NOAA significant earthquake database (https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/form?t=101650&s=1&d=1), lightly cleans it, and allows for various plots on both a timeline and a geographical view.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, leaflet, stringr, tidyr, testthat, lubridate
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
